### 5.3 Feed Page

**Layout — mobile first, max-width 480px centered on desktop:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│  ← today            🎙 📷  │  ← sticky header
├─────────────────────────────│
│  gym  reading  water  ...   │  ← habits strip (scrollable)
