│  11:32                      │
│  [image thumbnail]          │
│                             │
│  ...                        │
└─────────────────────────────┘
```

**Components needed:**
- `FeedHeader` — date nav + mic + camera icon buttons
- `HabitsStrip` — horizontal scrollable habit chips
- `AudioEntry` — waveform player + habit matches, tap to expand
- `ImageEntry` — thumbnail + habit matches, tap to expand
- `LogDetail` — full page view of a log, shows rewritten content +
  raw transcript/description + habit matches
- `DateNavigator` — back/forward by day

**Capture flow:**
- Mic button → browser MediaRecorder API → record audio →
  on stop upload to POST /api/v1/logs/audio
- Camera button → input type=file accept=image/* capture=camera →
  on select upload to POST /api/v1/logs/image
- Both show an inline loading state in the feed while processing

**Responsive rules:**
- Font size minimum 16px (prevents iOS zoom on input focus)
- Touch targets minimum 44px
- Bottom safe area padding for iPhone home indicator
- Sticky header uses backdrop-filter for scroll blur effect

### 5.4 Audio Player Component

Custom lightweight waveform player using Web Audio API:
- Static waveform bars generated from amplitude data
- Play/pause toggle
- Duration display
- No external audio library needed

