## Phase 7 — Digest

### 7.1 Digest Endpoint

```
GET /api/v1/digest?date=2025-01-01
```

Generates a digest for the given day by:
1. Fetching all logs for that day
2. Passing all rewritten content to Gemini
3. Gemini produces a structured summary

**Digest prompt:**

```
You are summarising a user's day from their personal log entries.
Below are all their log entries for {date}. Produce a warm, personal
summary covering:

1. What they did today (2-3 sentences)
2. Habits completed vs missed
3. One interesting pattern or observation
4. A one-line reflection to close

Keep it under 200 words. Warm and personal, not clinical.

Entries:
{all_rewritten_content}

Habits being tracked: {habit_names}
```

### 7.2 Email Send

```
POST /api/v1/digest/send
Body: { "date": "2025-01-01", "email": "user@email.com" }
```

Use any simple Go SMTP library or Resend API.
Email is plain text or minimal HTML — no heavy templates.

### 7.3 Digest UI

```
/digest

┌─────────────────────────────┐
│  ← today's digest           │
├─────────────────────────────│
│  friday, 17 jan             │
│                             │
│  [digest text from gemini]  │
│                             │
│  habits                     │
│  ✓ gym  ✓ reading           │
│  ✗ water  ✗ no sugar        │
│                             │
│  [send to email]  button    │
└─────────────────────────────┘
```

